1.2
log
@Update to:
* gkrellm 2.2.0
* mms 2.1.19
* mss 2.5
* sun 0.11.0
* volume 2.1.9
* wireless 2.0.3

This also updates the dependancy on gkrellm to a minimum of 2.2.0, since
there are several updates that require some of the new functions.

From: Peter Hessler <spambox@@theapt.org>
